Package: rsiscorar
Title: Interface to the SISCORAR Tidal Current Prediction System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Eduardo", "Leoni",
           email = "e.leoni@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0955-5232"))
Description: Provides an R interface to the Brazilian Navy's SISCORAR
    (Sistema de Correntes e Mares) tidal current prediction system.
    Wraps the official SISCORAR prediction executables (via Wine on
    macOS/Linux) to predict ocean currents for 5 Brazilian coastal
    bays using 142 tidal harmonics. Reads binary prediction files,
    queries currents at specific coordinates and times, and exports
    to GRIB2 and NetCDF formats for marine navigation software.
