Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements:
    SISCORAR 5.0 (https://www.marinha.mil.br/chm/dados-do-smm/corrente-de-mare),
    Wine (macOS/Linux only, for running Windows prediction executables),
    CDO and ecCodes (optional, for GRIB2 export)
